    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1" name="Fix 1: add default to commands">Edit `useKeyboardShortcuts.ts:15`: `{ commands, context, enabled = true }` → `{ commands = [], context, enabled = true }`. Add comment citing task 081 + reason.</step>
    <step order="2" name="Verify CommandBar test">Run `npx jest src/components/PageChrome/__tests__/CommandBar.test.tsx`. Suite must pass (23 tests). Previously crashed at startup.</step>
    <step order="3" name="Fix 2: untrack deploy artifacts">`git rm --cached -r deploy/api-publish/`. Verify `git ls-files deploy/api-publish/` returns 0. Verify `ls deploy/api-publish/` still shows files (disk unchanged).</step>
    <step order="4" name="Verify .gitignore covers it">`git check-ignore deploy/api-publish/Sprk.Bff.Api.dll` should succeed.</step>
    <step order="5" name="Full test suite regression">`npm test` in `@spaarke/ui-components` — expect 1074/1074 (was 1051 + 23 newly-unblocked from CommandBar).</step>
    <step order="6" name="Build regression">`dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/` — 0 errors.</step>
    <step order="7" name="Document">Write `projects/spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r4/notes/081-cleanup-residuals.md` capturing both fixes + verification.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
